00:00011162 D080            	   892: 	ADD.L	D0,D0
00:00011164 650001CC        	   893: 	BCS	QHOW		say "How?" if index is too big
00:00011168 D080            	   894: 	ADD.L	D0,D0
00:0001116A 650001C6        	   895: 	BCS	QHOW
00:0001116E 2F00            	   896: 	MOVE.L	D0,-(SP)	save the index
